ExecDesc.value: Microsoft Windows SharePoint Services Cross Site Scripting (IPv6 Version)

EngDesc.value: There exist a cross-site scripting vulnerability in Microsoft SharePoint. The flaw is due to lack of input validation when processing the URL request from client. The flaw may be exploited by malicious users to execute arbitrary HTML code on target user's web browser, within the context of a trusted web site. (IPv6 Version)
